synopsis.text: Dog s with human faces inhabit the distant Jinmen planet in the year 40XX, where one such canine operates as a detective from his office, offering free counsel to fellow dogs. Despite the scarcity of clients, this secret NEET stays busy engaging in debates about social networks with his chihuahua sister and friends, catching up on idol videos on Dog Tube, and attempting to dissuade Maltese from marking his territory at the entrance. Join this passionate human-faced dog and his troubled comrades in their unique adventures on Jinmen planet.
